Sessions Subscription Gate
[x] **Frontend - session-list.component.ts**: Inject `SubscriptionService`, add `canManageSessions = signal(false)`, call `subscriptionService.load()` in `ngOnInit` and set signal via `hasFeature('session_notes')`
[x] **Frontend - session-list.component.html**: Conditionally hide the "Add Session" button (`[buttonText]="canManageSessions() ? 'Add Session' : ''"`) and show an upgrade notice link to `/billing` when `!canManageSessions()`
[x] **Frontend - session-form.component.ts**: Inject `SubscriptionService`, guard new-session creation (when no `id` param) — redirect to `/sessions` with a toast error if `hasFeature('session_notes')` is false
[x] **Backend - sessions/service.go**: Add `RequireFeature(userID, "session_notes")` check to `GetAll` (or at minimum to `Update`) to match the barn pattern